https://my.plaid.com/
). The products and services provided to you by the Application are governed by a separate agreement between you and the provider of the Application ("
Application Terms
"). We have no responsibility for the products and services provided to you by or through the Application and will not be liable to you for any harm, damage or loss arising from your use of the products and services provided by or through the Application.
2.2. Our Services will allow you to obtain financial information from your online bank or payment account ("
Payment Account
") (account information services).
