At Plaid, we understand the importance of privacy and transparency. The purpose of this Candidate Privacy Notice (‚ÄúNotice‚Äù) is to explain how Plaid Inc. and its subsidiaries, including Plaid Financial Ltd. and Plaid, B.V. (collectively, ‚ÄúPlaid‚Äù, ‚Äúwe‚Äù, ‚Äúour‚Äù, or ‚Äúus‚Äù), collect, use, and share personal data and information from and about potential candidates (‚Äúyou‚Äù or ‚Äúyour‚Äù) for positions with Plaid (‚ÄúCandidate Information‚Äù).
