This Cookie Policy (‚ÄúPolicy‚Äù) explains how Plaid Inc. and its subsidiaries, including Plaid Financial Ltd., Plaid Consumer Reporting Agency, Inc., and Plaid, B.V., (collectively, ‚Äúwe‚Äù, ‚Äúour‚Äù, or ‚Äúus‚Äù), and trusted third parties, use cookies on our websites and other online services (collectively the ‚ÄúServices‚Äù), as well as your choices related to those cookies. Please review this Policy to learn more about the types of cookies we use, why we use them, and how you can control or limit the use of cookies.
